Source code
-----------

The complete corresponding source code for this Windows build is
available at:

  https://github.com/panibor/kpat
  https://invent.kde.org/games/kpat  (upstream)

Build reproducibility
---------------------

This binary was produced by the GitHub Actions workflow referenced above,
running on `windows-2022` with KDE Craft. To reproduce locally on Windows,
see README.windows.md.

